<ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Randolph W. McElroy</ENAMEX> , a vice chairman of this bank - holding company , was named to the additional position of chairman of its principal unit , <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG">Sovran Bank</ENAMEX> .
Mr. <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">McElroy</ENAMEX> , <ENAMEX TYPE="DATE">54 years old</ENAMEX> , will remain president and chief executive officer of the unit .
